Comment: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.51,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/--------START---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:07.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:09.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何他会出现在此地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:15.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,准备离开这里伊斯多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:16.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她俩拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我在里面发现了一条小道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:24.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,记得还我人 带利息的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:26.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等离开这里再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:32.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,憋 死 人 了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:33.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,阿呼 出来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:37.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子他跟邪教徒是敌对关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:40.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此也不能说明他是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:44.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘了吗 他是我等同胞的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:45.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:48.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要连黑色剑士也一起逮捕吗 法尔纳塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:54.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已完全进入战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不投降者统统杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 法尔纳塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色剑士...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:02:59.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若继续袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只会增加我军伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无疑问 他们就是邪教徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:08.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,连黑色剑士也一起歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:12.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我等乃神托付利剑之人 怎能如此胆小!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:14.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全军出击!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:18.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以毒攻毒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别东张西望 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,带路 伊斯多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:26.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能让他逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:26.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,服了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:31.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不会交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:46.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女...交媾...我的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:47.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们退后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:05.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若没有高特的盔甲 脊柱早就断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,宰了它做羊肉火锅!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:14.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛 你带上她俩先走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:15.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 你可别翘辫子啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 把她放下!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一个个地吊我胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有你这种假使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:48.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说明骷髅大叔并没有说谎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:49.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:53.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,踢死! 撞死!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:58.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能把她留在这种鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:01.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定要...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...带走她!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咩! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,射中一两箭也没什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:29.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只能试试看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:36.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:07.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,炸弹 真是管用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:29.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如此混战 大将亲自上阵实在太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请您先撤退到洞口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,走 法尔纳塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:37.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾桑!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来交给我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:41.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放手!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:43.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,纹章官 跟我来!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高! 在哪?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没有掉下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恭候多时了 黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:07.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:26.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:29.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在先别向我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有路啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:38.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是那些邪教徒为求解脱跳崖自尽的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 猴吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这个的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我会拉着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟卸货那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意就跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:58.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,问题在于这位姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本来我的信条是让人拔不出剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:19.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,反正在这里你挥不了剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抢在你前头真是太正确了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:29.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可以占据如此地利和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是神明庇佑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:33.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一群人围攻你简直愚蠢透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你拔出那把剑砍倒10人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:45.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,战局便会瞬间改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:50.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为恐惧所感染的战友比敌人更防不胜防
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,何等精明的家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完全找不到拔剑的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对法尔纳塞小姐来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的存在有点刺激过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有请你消失!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不往下看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不往下看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不往下看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要摔下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:30.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 千万别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正面射过去的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:57.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,狭窄且松动的脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的身躯再加上沉重的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为岩壁所限制的惯用手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切都成了你的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他不仅懂策略
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剑术亦高得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:13.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,变化自如完全看不穿他的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:16.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比刚才那个假使徒更难对付
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:22.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没时间在这种地方磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在担心那两位姑娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我身后战友应该布下了包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:32.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她们已是插翅难飞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:37.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不令你更焦急的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:43.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正面对决我没信心能赢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:55.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有够乱来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:58.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,乱来? 你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:02.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若我抽剑回来 你的手指...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就看反射神经跟腕力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 我的手皮很厚!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,居然那样避开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:39.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还顺手偷走了一枚炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只看过一次的武器还能娴熟使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难啃的骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,狡猾如狐的家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,实在不该明知不可为而为之啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:07.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是...竟然不自量力去挑战他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,带了这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅抓不到黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还让他进了洞 成何体统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:23.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 属下大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:26.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听这些借口!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火气真大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:39.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我说怎么不对劲 那个跟屁虫去哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:55.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 刚才好像...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:13.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就快到了 加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸? 约阿希...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:26.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:27.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:31.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,约阿希姆 你还活...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是邪教徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的岩石后面有邪教徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:37.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:41.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,约阿希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:44.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 大姐姐快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,发呆会被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢 卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:01.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 伊斯多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死就死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:21.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,报告 邪教徒基本镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那黑色剑士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在被捕的人以及尸体中都没发现他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那位姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑色剑士冲进去救人的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上我们还没回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就什么都别管直接离开阿尔比安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:45.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞的话会被那些官兵抓走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:47.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝你别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:54.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅不安全还会成为累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你说得真直接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:59.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错 这可不是女人该干的事情 露加大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:00.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我自有我的理由!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要连本带利拿回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:11.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我来晚了 但这次不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:16.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是只有你才能担心那些孩子 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:20.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我在阿尔比安修道院有点门路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:23.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若一切顺利也许不用流血便能救出她们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,随你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还是死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,关在那座塔里根本毫无办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:41.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太死心眼了 露加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:43.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是正直得来又傻傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:49.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果露加姐姐他们没有回来的话我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:56.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请保佑露加姐姐他们平安归来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会出现倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是由失去光芒的太阳所笼罩之地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,投射至遥远人世间的倒影罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:22.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等已在因果循环当中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:29.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:32.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多人 她们的气息也变得模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:35.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那里好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是蝙蝠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:39.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是如此宽敞的寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:45.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可这窒息感是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:46.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妖魔的巢穴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:48.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此也没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多更污秽的东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:52.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,必须快点找到卡思嘉她们才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦 你是魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能用魔术逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:24.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说啊 如果不赶快逃离会出大事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是够了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:34.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自从遇见你之后就没有一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全是倒楣事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾你的人是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可为何...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何...受伤的总是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:58.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们其中一个出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都行 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:20.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不用你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就你吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的同伴被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然一点也不护着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只顾着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:36.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会饶恕这种卑鄙之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:37.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:40.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快点出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦 我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:55.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:57.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:00.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:02.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...因为我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使抛下啥都不懂的艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也想自己得救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:15.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都变成了这副样子 说不定快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那就更不应该了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太渣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是报应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:32.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,据我们调查 你们当中出现了真正的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:33.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:35.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其他女的都审问过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:39.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们当中有一个就是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:40.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是指艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若是马上一五一十地跟他们说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,或许不用吃苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:49.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,任谁到最后都只会为自己打算
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要我中途抛弃他人 恕难从命!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:20:59.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你还是艾伦我都不会不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:08.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请赐我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:11.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点便足够
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:15.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的勇气 请赐我一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:33.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊啊啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:37.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:41.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:44.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:49.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到啊 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:04.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟 近看还真够大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:06.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是寺院倒不如说是城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:10.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 别嚷嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:14.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 脖子隐隐作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:16.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:19.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是更怪异的...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:21.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很危险...!
